text: Sebastian "Baste" Zimmerman Duterte (; ; born November 3, 1987) is a Filipino politician. He is the mayor of Davao City since 2022. Before, he was deputy mayor from 2019 until 2022. He is the youngest son of former President Rodrigo Duterte. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Filipino mayors
title: Sebastian Duterte
